# Configuration for less(1)
# Run "lesskey" to produce a ".less" file from this source file.
#Reference:  https://github.com/insidewhy/colemak/issues/5
#command
h    left-scroll

# qwerty
l    right-scroll

# colemak
i    right-scroll
n    forw-line
N    forw-line-force
e    back-line
E    back-line-force
k    repeat-search
\ek  repeat-search-all
K    reverse-search
\eK  reverse-search-all
